The '''Fântânele Power Station''' is a large [[thermal power plant]] located in [[Mureş County]] having 5 generation groups of 50&nbsp;[[Watt#Megawatt|MW]]<ref>[http://www.standard.ro/articol_59760/22_de_companii__interesate_de_cet_urile_progresu_si_fantanele.html 22 de companii interesate de CET Progresu su Fantanele {{ro}}]</ref> having a total [[electricity]] generation capacity of 250 [[Megawatt|MW]].
